title: Joe DeRosa
description: Joe DeRosa (Comedy Central! CHEAT film and book! Comedy!) is one of Pete's best friends and funniest people ever and Pete was so glad to get to sit down with him at his place in NYC and gab like guys. So much gabbin. Laughs, bits, riffing bits, laser. All of it. ENJOY, WEIRDOS!!
